      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust E46 M3 powered by the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS variable valve timing. This driver-focused example has received critical preventative maintenance, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive cooling system overhaul. The 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp, tactile shifts, delivering power to the rear wheels through the factory M-variable limited-slip differential. The suspension retains its factory-spec geometry with refreshed bushings for precise turn-in and communicative feedback. While the exterior shows minor age-appropriate patina, the powertrain and chassis remain in excellent working order, offering a pure, analog driving experience for the discerning enthusiast.",
